</head>
<body>
<table style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; border-collapse: collapse;">
    <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">
            <a href="#" style="color: #00466a; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">
                <img src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/previews/007/438/687/original/illustration-of-a-pharmacy-health-pharmacy-logo-free-vector.jpg" alt="Your Brand Logo" style="width: 150px; height: auto;" />
            </a>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px;">
            <p>Hi <%= locals.name %>,</p>
            <p>Welcome to the exciting world of <%= locals.appName%>! To complete your verification and unlock all our amazing features, please enter the following one-time password (OTP):</p>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="text-align: center; background-color: #00466a; color: #fff; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px;">
            <h2 style="margin: 0;"><%= locals.otp %></h2>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px;">
            <p>This code will expire in [duration], so hurry and enter it now.</p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">If you didn't request this code, please disregard this email and contact us immediately.</p>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
            <a href="#" style="background-color: #00466a; color: #fff; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 5px;">Verify Now</a>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
            <p>Already have an account?</p>
            <p><a href="#" style="color: #00466a;">Sign in here</a></p>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
